Dialogue: 100,0:00:00.88,0:00:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bun! Pune-l aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.93,0:00:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poftim. Ai grijă!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așteaptă puțin. Bun!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.67,0:00:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lord Hayate...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.15,0:00:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,mulțumită ție, Gon și oamenii lui vor fi duși în închisoarea din capitala regală,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.61,0:00:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,iar grupul nostru, care se ocupă de transport, va putea pleca în siguranță.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doar mi-am făcut datoria
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.81,0:00:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ca persoană în serviciul acestui regat.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.73,0:00:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am încredere în natura ta sinceră, \Ndeci vreau să te rog ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă este ceva ce pot face...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Această scrisoare este \Npentru tatăl tău, lordul Gouki.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.91,0:00:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă ai putea să i-o \Ndai din partea mea...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.99,0:00:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatălui meu?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este o scrisoare foarte importantă.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.45,0:00:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aș aprecia foarte mult \Ndacă i-ai da-o personal.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.87,0:00:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.43,0:00:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să merg în următorul \Nsat ca să le verific taxele,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.29,0:00:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,deci nu mă voi putea întoarce în capitală până nu termin,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.65,0:00:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar i-o voi da negreșit.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.11,0:00:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este în regulă acest lucru?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.53,0:01:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți mulțumesc foarte mult.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drum bun!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:10.85,0:01:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și astfel...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}am pornit cu toții și ne-am separat de lordul Hayate pe drum.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.72,0:01:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Noi restul am reușit să ajungem în capitala Regatului Karasuki după șapte zile.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aici vom sta.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă vă pierdeți, nu veți \Nreuși să vă mai întoarceți,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.65,0:03:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,așa că atunci când vreți să plecați, asigurați-vă că mergeți cu cineva care cunoaște capitala.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt nevoit să plec, deci voi \Nlăsa restul în seama voastră.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio, Shin, ați vrea să veniți cu mine?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și eu?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mișcați-vă.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acel nemernic.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voiam să-l omor.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu e un sfârșit prea satisfăcător, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.50,0:03:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mai sta așa supărat. \NE timpul să te înveselești puțin.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.57,0:03:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Î-Încetează, maestre vânător! \NNu-mi face asta în fața lui!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trei porții de kamutan! \NMulțumesc pentru așteptare!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.86,0:04:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa arată kamutanul?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.13,0:04:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? Nu ai mai mâncat \Nkamutan până acum, Rio?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nu.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te vei mai putea opri din \Nmâncat odată ce ai gustat.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.51,0:04:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prima oară când ai mâncat aveai lacrimi în ochi, nu-i așa, Shin?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presupun...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.11,0:04:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De regulă, kamutanul se mănâncă sorbind!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide, Rio. Mănâncă sau se va răci.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine. Să mâncăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este foarte bun!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumim!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi pentru ce ai făcut pentru Sayo.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.27,0:04:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.62,0:04:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, așa este.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.43,0:04:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să mă asigur că va mânca și ea asta sau vom ajunge să ne certăm din nou.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am luat tot ce trebuia, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da. Mersi mult, Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar să-mi ceara mie, care nu cunosc orașul, să merg la cumpărături...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu am nicio idee ce le trece prin cap.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai vrea să mâncăm niște kamutan după ce terminăm?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.99,0:05:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.19,0:05:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin mi-a cerut să te duc acolo dacă ne rămâne niște timp liber.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fratele meu ți-a cerut asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-a spus că ți-a cerut să-i faci,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.73,0:05:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar v-ați certat deoarece tu ai spus că nu-l poți prepara fiindcă nu ai mâncat niciodată.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A spus că vrea să se asigure că nu vei mai putea spune asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamne, ce mai mâncăcios.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.88,0:05:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar eu cred că el doar vrea ca tu să ai șansa să mănânci kamutan.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.83,0:05:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este un frate mai mare grijuliu, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, așa este.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You there, young man!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce spui de un cadou pentru drăguța ta prietenă?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nu sunt prietena lui sau ceva!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, vai, am presupun asta deoarece arătați așa de bine împreună.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar ce spuneți de un suvenir din capitală?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.47,0:06:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avem niște produse foarte drăguțe, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.03,0:06:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa este. Din moment ce suntem deja aici...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, e ceva ce-ți place?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? S-Sunt în regulă!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai făcut multe lucruri pentru mine, deci nu ezita să alegi.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, da.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.05,0:06:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Domnișoară, în momente ca acesta, curtoazia unei doamne este arătată prin acceptarea cadoului.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te pricepi la afaceri, nu-i așa, domnișoară?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.83,0:06:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, domnișoară, ai un ochi bine format!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acela e unul dintre cele mai elegante obiecte ale noastre.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai dori să-l încerci?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce părere ai, domnule?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți stă foarte bine cu el.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa? Ți se potrivește perfect!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.10,0:06:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar prețul e destul de ridicat, adică două monede pătrate, mici de argint.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Monede pătrate, mici de argint?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Foarte bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Rio, este în regulă! \NNu-mi trebuie...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aș putea oferi o mică reducere.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu voi negocia niciodată prețul cadoului unei domnișoare.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impresionant!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În acest caz, ar fi trebuit să ridic puțin mai mult prețul.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mergem?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Î-Îți mulțumesc foarte mult!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Domnișoară!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dă tot ce poți ca să-l faci al tău!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.99,0:07:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mie-mi pare că vei avea ceva competiție pentru el.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dă-mi drumul, ticălosule!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cineva să-l oprească!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La o parte din drum!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.85,0:07:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, ești bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.89,0:07:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Da, sunt bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Domnișoară Komomo!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pare să fie inconștientă, dar nu cred că viața-i este în pericol.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sincerele mele scuze. Incompetența mea iremediabilă a permis acest lucru.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă vrei să-ți ceri scuze, \Nfă-o față de ea când se trezește.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce se întâmplă?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce se petrece?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Faceți loc!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să mergem, Sayo.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.42,0:08:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? Dar... ești sigur de asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, vreau să evit orice fel de probleme.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.96,0:08:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așteaptă, te rog!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunteți bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ați fost rănite, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Komomo aproape a fost răpită?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am avut noroc că nu au reușit.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.52,0:08:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi s-a spus că tânărul care a salvat-o pe Komomo și i-a prins pe răpitori
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a plecat imediat de la locul întâmplărilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci spuneai că vrei să vorbim doar noi doi?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.78,0:08:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamna Yuba mi-a încredițat această scrisoare ca să ți-o aduc, tată.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.10,0:08:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A spus că este o scrisoare importantă și ar trebui să ți-o aduc personal.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg. De la Yuba.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai întâlnit o persoană pe nume Rio?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ne-am întors!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, bine ați revenit!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Frate mai mare, kamutanul a fost foarte bun!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.43,0:09:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when we get back to the village, \Nthis time you'll make some for me, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, where did you get that hairpin?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, well...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go put these away.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lord Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lord Hayate?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am called Saga Gouki.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Kayoko.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.37,0:10:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are husband and wife, and we \Nwere both once attendants of your mother...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.64,0:10:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady Karasuki Ayame.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.42,0:10:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Karasuki... Ayame?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your surprise is understandable.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.30,0:10:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lord Rio, your mother was of the royal \Nfamily of the Kingdom of Karasuki.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother... was royalty?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.79,0:10:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, shall I tell you about my \Nconnection to your father Zen, Lord Rio?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened over twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.55,0:10:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, the Karasuki Kingdom was at \Nwar with our neighboring kingdom, Rokuren.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.78,0:10:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zen volunteered to be a soldier.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.04,0:10:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zen had a natural gift for both \Nthe spirit arts and martial arts.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.47,0:10:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His Majesty the King soon bestowed \Nupon him the rank of warrior-noble.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.64,0:11:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, he had a bout with me.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His skills were the real thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.73,0:11:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.74,0:11:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I strongly recommended that he should \Nguard members of the royal family.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.29,0:11:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am sure you can already guess that the \Nmember of the royal family he guarded...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...was Lady Ayame.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.08,0:11:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady Ayame took a liking to Zen.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.27,0:11:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was at that time that a truce was \Nnegotiated with the Kingdom of Rokuren.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the ceremony celebrating the truce,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.29,0:11:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the prince who had come as ambassador \Ntook a liking to Lady Ayame,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and tried to have his attendants abduct her.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zen kept them from completing their plan,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the prince resented the fact that \Nhis attendant had been killed.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the truce were to be finalized, \Nthe prince demanded Zen's execution,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.11,0:12:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a political marriage to Lady Ayame.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.57,0:12:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, the thought of \Nit makes my blood seethe.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.70,0:12:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why my mother and \Nfather ran away together?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His Majesty the King \Narranged for it in secret,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the two of them left our country.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.96,0:12:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so time flowed on, with no\N news or contact with them.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But today, I received \Ncorrespondence from Lady Yuba.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.30,0:12:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And having looked upon your honored \Ncountenance, Lord Rio, I am certain.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There can be no doubt that you are their son.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:40.37,0:12:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lord Rio, tomorrow, will you\N come to the castle?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His Majesty the King and \NHer Highness the Queen...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.71,0:12:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is my dearest wish that you \Nand they might meet, Lord Rio.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of them... and me?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please. Please, I beg of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I will.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.11,0:13:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you are Rio?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am honored to meet you, Your Majesties.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:15.88,0:13:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,King Homura, Queen Shizuku, my name is Rio.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a meeting with \Nour darling grandchild.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible for you \Nto be less formal with us?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.27,0:13:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you permit it, then... I will do my best.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, will you take a seat?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:37.82,0:13:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio, you really do look exactly like Ayame.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.45,0:13:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel that it's you, Queen Shizuku, \Nwho looks just like my mother.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, do you think so?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio, will you tell us?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell us about Ayame and Zen.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.89,0:13:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.10,0:14:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To cut straight to the conclusion, \Nboth of them have already died.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:04.71,0:14:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is how they died and how they lived\N that we would like to hear.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:11.94,0:14:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father died when I was \Ntoo young to know him.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.96,0:14:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother was a kind person \Nwho never stopped smiling.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:21.78,0:14:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She never showed me her \Ngrief at my father's death.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.56,0:14:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were by no means affluent, \Nbut every day was a happy one.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.39,0:14:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I was five, my mother passed away.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.21,0:14:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were five?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did Ayame die?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.30,0:14:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I tell you the truth, it will \Nbe incredibly painful to hear.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, we want to know.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.92,0:14:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was killed...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,right in front of me.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who killed her \Nis a man named Lucius.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently he had worked with \Nmy father as an adventurer.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.18,0:15:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After my father's death, \Nhe'd helped us in many ways.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that day...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.69,0:15:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back soon. If anyone you \Ndon't know comes, you stay inside.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio, it's me. It's Lucius.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you open the door?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.76,0:15:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this world, there are demons \Nwho masquerade in human skins.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:39.39,0:15:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one fact smarter now.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Master Lucius?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.60,0:15:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you done to him? \NLet go! Let go right now!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.37,0:16:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is my last memory of my mother.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could this be...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.77,0:16:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how have you lived since then?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.43,0:16:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I woke up, I'd been left in the slums.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stayed there and lived as an orphan.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though that was only until I was seven.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened then?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:35.90,0:16:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was... an incident where \NI happened to rescue someone
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.27,0:16:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of importance to the kingdom.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:40.86,0:16:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was allowed to attend an educational \Ninstitution run by the kingdom.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In our kingdom,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.88,0:16:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we have a school for the court nobles \Nand some of the warrior-nobles, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone around me was of similar rank.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must have been difficult for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was treated a little harshly,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there were people who treated me well, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.91,0:17:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to them, I can hold my head high \Nand say my days there were enjoyable.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I attended that school until I was twelve,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.33,0:17:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then I set out for this land that my \Nmother had promised to show me one day.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayame made such a promise?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.01,0:17:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both you and Ayame must \Nharbor a deep hatred for us.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.39,0:17:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think my mother was grateful to you...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for being able to marry my father.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:29.35,0:17:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would make no sense for me to \Nhate you in the face of that, would it?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Rio...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man who killed Ayame...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.23,0:17:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can forgive him.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man is the one person \NI will never forgive.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.66,0:17:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, do you hope for revenge?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once, that was all \NI thought about. It kept me alive.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But revenge doesn't create anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And my mother wouldn't want it, either.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've thought those things, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, if I ever met that man...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With these hands, I would...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know, Rio...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.65,0:18:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you travel the path of revenge, \Nwhat you will find is hell.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.02,0:18:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can still turn back. \NWill you proceed, even so?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:19.61,0:18:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am determined to proceed, even so.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:22.06,0:18:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's necessary, I would not \Nhesitate to dirty my own hands.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.76,0:18:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But before that, I would \Nlike you to spar with Gouki.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With Lord Gouki?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no match for Gouki in \Nany of the surrounding kingdoms.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.74,0:18:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is the Karasuki Kingdom's \Nstrongest warrior.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:40.36,0:18:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man named Lucius must be very skilled.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:43.83,0:18:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Considering his hideous nature, \Nhe may even have killed Zen.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Gouki?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:52.85,0:18:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to admit it, \Nbut it is definitely possible.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:56.80,0:19:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you are to one day face Lucius, then you\N will require strength, will you not?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:03.90,0:19:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he is willing to teach me \Nthe basics, then, yes, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father! Mother! Welcome home!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aoi, what is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:17.49,0:19:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-The person you're with is the \None who saved Lady Komomo!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this? Is that right?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:27.42,0:19:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we will proceed with combat forms.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both parties, at the ready.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your potential is frightening.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to think that in terms of both \Nphysicality and experience,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you haven't yet reached your prime...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Training is the one thing \NI've always kept up.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've done well!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:05.46,0:20:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He combines sword work \Nwith weaponless styles.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impressive!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be... Father is at a disadvantage?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is thrilling!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magical energy is gathering around his sword?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Father! You can't be thinking of using...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hidden Skill, First Blade...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Air Slash!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.41,0:20:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,End of match!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:43.85,0:20:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bout goes to Lord Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've lost this one.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.43,0:20:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Father has...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's incredible.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:01.64,0:21:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.84,0:21:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had thought to have you train under Gouki, \Nbut I see my solicitude was unnecessary.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.53,0:21:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Having this experience before \Nheading to Beltrum was invaluable.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.57,0:21:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time left,\N but is there anything you wish to ask?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:22.94,0:21:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a cousin who lives in the \Nvillage where I've been staying.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.97,0:21:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to tell her \Nabout my lineage, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.29,0:21:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. We will trust your judgment in this.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Rio?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.02,0:21:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ruri, Sir Rio is...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:52.62,0:21:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, Mother... I can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.12,0:22:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to live, in order \Nto protect what's precious,
Dialogue: 100,0:22:00.10,0:22:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will accept the ugliness \Nwithin me and move forward.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Deciziile fiecăruia."
